{
  "_comment": [
    "Grafana dashboard panels for rollback audit observability.",
    "Drop these into an existing dashboard via 'Import JSON' or merge into a",
    "fresh dashboard JSON under .panels[]. Counters/histograms emitted by",
    "go/data_service/internal/metrics/metrics.go (rollback_*, cross_scene_*).",
    "",
    "Six panels — three columns × two rows:",
    "  Row 1 (operational at-a-glance):",
    "    1. Rollback rate by scope (player|zone|server) — usage volume",
    "    2. Rollback outcome split (ok|partial|failed) — health",
    "    3. Players affected (counter delta over time) — blast radius",
    "  Row 2 (forensics):",
    "    4. Orphan characters cleaned by scope — zone/server merge hygiene",
    "    5. Cross-scene transition latency by phase (release|save|load|total)",
    "    6. Cross-scene transition outcome split — Single Writer health",
    "",
    "Alerting (configure in Grafana, not in the JSON):",
    "  - rollback_total{outcome='failed'} rate > 0.01/s for 5m → page on-call",
    "  - rollback_total{scope='server'} > 0 in any 1m → page (full-server",
    "    rollback should never happen unprompted)",
    "  - cross_scene_transition_total{outcome!='ok'} share > 1% for 10m → page",
    "",
    "Source metrics:",
    "  See go/data_service/internal/metrics/metrics.go (lines 72-90 rollback;",
    "  lines 53-69 cross-scene). Subsystem prefix is 'data_service'."
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "title": "Rollback Rate by Scope",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Rate of rollback attempts by scope. player = single-player corrective; zone = mass action; server = full-server reset (should be vanishingly rare).",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (scope) (rate(data_service_rollback_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{scope}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 25,
            "stacking": { "mode": "normal" }
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 8, "h": 8 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Rollback Outcome Split",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "ok/partial/failed share over time. Sustained partial+failed > 1% suggests data plane (Redis/Kafka) instability — investigate before next rollback attempt.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (outcome) (rate(data_service_rollback_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{outcome}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 35,
            "stacking": { "mode": "percent" }
          },
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "failed" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "partial" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "ok" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "x": 8, "y": 0, "w": 8, "h": 8 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Players Affected (delta)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Number of players whose data was actually restored, per scope. Spikes correspond to zone/server rollback events; player-scope is steady single-digit per-minute corrective work.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (scope) (increase(data_service_rollback_players_affected_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{scope}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 80
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "x": 16, "y": 0, "w": 8, "h": 8 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Orphan Characters Cleaned by Scope",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Players created after the rollback target_time and scrubbed during zone/server rollback. Non-zero on player-scope rollback would be a bug — flag immediately.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (scope) (increase(data_service_rollback_orphans_cleaned_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{scope}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "bars",
            "fillOpacity": 80
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 8, "h": 8 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Cross-Scene Transition Latency (p95) by Phase",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "Per-phase p95 latency. release = old-scene flush; save = data_service write; load = new-scene read; total = end-to-end. Sustained total > 1s = Single Writer pause is hurting players.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (phase, le) (rate(data_service_cross_scene_transition_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{phase}} p95"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 10
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "x": 8, "y": 8, "w": 8, "h": 8 }
    },
    {
      "title": "Cross-Scene Transition Outcome Split",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "description": "ok / release_timeout / save_failed / load_failed / aborted. Anything other than ok is a Single-Writer hazard — crashed transitions can leave a player flagged at two scenes.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (outcome) (rate(data_service_cross_scene_transition_total[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{outcome}}"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 35,
            "stacking": { "mode": "percent" }
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "ok" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "x": 16, "y": 8, "w": 8, "h": 8 }
    }
  ]
}
